  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-stellar\">single-use</span> receiver that scans for distress signals on <span class=\"name name-technology\">freighter frequencies</span>. Derelict or abandoned freighters often contain <span class=\"name name-stellar\">high-value salvage</span>.<br><br>Select the Receiver and use Tune Signal (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>) to begin the location process.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一个<span class=\"name name-stellar\">一次性</span>接收器扫描<span class=\"name name-technology\">货船频率</span>中的求救信号。荒废或废弃货船通常拥有<span class=\"name name-stellar\">高价值的回收物</span>。<br><br>选择接收器并使用调谐信号（<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>）即可开始定位流程。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種<span class=\"name name-stellar\">單次使用</span>的接收器，用來掃描<span class=\"name name-technology\">貨船頻率</span>是否有求救訊號。棄守或廢棄的貨船，通常載有<span class=\"name name-stellar\">高價值回收物</span>。<br><br>選擇接收器，再使用「調整訊號頻率」（<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>）功能，即可開始尋找。"
  },
